scollector
==========

Install scollector standalone binary and start it under supervisor
control.

scollector is a replacement for OpenTSDB's TCollector.
  http://bosun.org/scollector/


Dependencies
============

This role has a dependency on supervisor declared in meta.


Role variables
==============

scollector_tsd_host
-------------------

TSD endpoint to connect to. Supports TLS and HTTP Basic Auth.

  https://user:password@example.com/


scollector_tags
---------------

Dict of extra tags to send with every metrics.

  cluster: production
  othertag: 7
